Main KPI 11

In this dashboard the main KPI's are :-

  • Total Cases 

 DAX calculation for total cases   

               Total Cases = SUM('COVID-19 In US'[positive Increase])

Steps for this report

Go to report page to work on card for Total cases.

1. Drag and drop card from visualization.

2. Drag and drop Total cases measure from measure table.

3. Add a title text and use same format through out the dashboard.  (Refer step 4)

4. Customize Data label

  •     Color - white, 10% darker
  •     Display units auto
  •     Text size - 15pt
  •     Font family - Arial

5. Category - off

6.  Boarder - on

  • Color - white 30% darker




  • Total Deaths

DAX calculation for total deaths :  

                Total Deaths = SUM('COVID-19 in US'[death Increase])

Steps for this report

Go to report page to work on card for Total deaths.

1. Drag and drop card from visualization.

2. Drag and drop Total deaths measure from measure table.

3. Add a title text and use same format through out the dashboard.  (Refer step 4)

4. Customize Data label

  •     Color -  #f9bba9, theme color 8, 60% lighter
  •     Display units auto
  •     Text size - 15pt
  •     Font family - Arial

5. Category - off

6.  Boarder - on

  • Color - white 30% darker
